(14,1,"2019-05-29 00:18:41","2019-05-29 00:18:41","<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>About Us</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Immo-Comm real estate commission advances was built in 2018\nby two entrepreneurs with experience around technology and financial markets.\nOur aim was to better understand how commissions are paid out across various\nindustry and see how we could provide value by changing the way people earn\ntheir living. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Significant search led us to one industry to target; real\nestate. Because of the nature of the assets being exchanged, many real estate\nagents are expected to wait for their commission far after their job is done.\nBy leveraging technology and financial engineering, we are changing the way\nagents get paid and have a host of future ideas which we hope will help\nrevolutionize an industry that is in desperate need for a change! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","About Us","","publish","closed","closed","","about-us","","","2019-06-11 23:57:03","2019-06-11 23:57:03","",0,"http://immocomm.test/?page_id=14",0,"page","",0),
