(82,3,"2019-06-04 17:11:07","2019-06-04 17:11:07","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>My first post content is here</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Being a real estate agent is one of\nthe most challenging jobs anyone could ever ask for. A daily barrage of calls,\nemails and intense negotiations follow almost every single deal. Whether you’re\nselling started condos or million dollar listings, the challenges are the same\nand always exist!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As deal flow grows, your time\nbecomes more and more challenging and the so called grow or bust effect quickly\nmanifests. Many agents tackle this by hiring and growing their business but the\nnature of real estate leads to a challenge; how do you grow your business\neffectively?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>You can either take the traditional\nroute financing the business yourself and weathering the tough cashflow periods\nand endless closing times or you can turn to a commission advance! </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By leveraging your existing purchase\noffers, you can get up to 100% of your commission advanced helping you grow\nyour business faster than ever. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The key is finding what works!\nWhether that’s hiring an assistant, taking on junior brokers or leading a\nmarketing campaign, all these require funds. That’s where Immo-Comm comes in. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By taking our commission advances,\nyou are able to grow your business faster than ever, hire support staff and\nfocus on what matters most; closing more deals!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A commission advance from Immo-Comm\nis an easy process and, with industry leading pricing and no hidden fees we are\nyour obvious choice. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Try us once and see how we can help.\nApply today. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","How Commission advances help you grow your business","","publish","open","open","","post-1","","","2019-06-14 19:42:13","2019-06-14 19:42:13","",0,"http://immocomm.test/?p=82",0,"post","",0),
