(85,3,"2019-06-04 21:34:21","2019-06-04 21:34:21","<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Contrary to popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is not simply random text. It has roots in a piece of classical Latin literature from 45 BC, making it over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a Latin professor at Hampden-Sydney College in Virginia, looked up one of the more obscure Latin words, consectetur, from a Lorem Ipsum passage, and going through the cites of the word in classical literature, discovered the undoubtable source. Lorem Ipsum comes from sections 1.10.32 and 1.10.33 of \"de Finibus Bonorum et Malorum\" (The Extremes of Good and Evil) by Cicero, written in 45 BC. This book is a treatise on the theory of ethics, very popular during the Renaissance. The first line of Lorem Ipsum, \"Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet..\", comes from a line in section 1.10.32.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Growing as an real estate agent can be one of the biggest\nchallenges you face. In this day and age, there are so many agents to choose\nfrom. How do you stand out from the crowd and how do you get clients faster and\nmore effectively? The answer is simple in theory but hard to execute; make sure\neveryone knows you!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether that’s networking events, door knocking or calling\nexpired listings, there is a multitude of ways to get your name out there and\nmake sure people know you. All these things require time however, and time away\nfrom your current clients may potentially hurt you while also being exhausting.\n</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Luckily, we live in the golden age of marketing whether a\nfew dollars strategically spent can have a major impact on your business and\ngetting you known! You could be the most knowledgeable, and trustworthy broker\nbut, if people don’t know you, that phone won’t ring for new business!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>So how does one effectively market online and why should I\neven consider spending the money? The answer is why any business spends money;\nto earn a return. By effectively spend on marketing yourself, you are ensuring\nyou are out there in people’s minds and, with an effective strategy, you can\nshowcase your talents and stand out from the crowd. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>But how does a commission advance from Immo-Comm help me?\nThe answer is simple; if you’re waiting for your commission for 90+days, you\nare missing out on potential buyers and sellers during that time. By paying a\nsmall fee (often a few dollars) you can get your commission advanced today and\ninvest in marketing yourself. Imagine spending 75$ to get your commission\nadvanced and landing just one client from a marketing campaign would you call\nthat money well spent? How much does one client represent in terms of earnings?\nOnce you understand the power you can yield with an advance, you can quickly\ngrow your business and close more deals. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://www.immocomm.co/apply\"><strong>Apply </strong></a>today and see how we can help you grow your business. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->","Realtor Commission advances and how they help you grow your business","","publish","open","open","","post-2","","","2019-06-14 19:42:04","2019-06-14 19:42:04","",0,"http://immocomm.test/?p=85",0,"post","",0),
